NAME
  thread.setFilter
  
CALLS
  thread.setFilter(string: threadUid, string: filter)
  
RETURNS
  boolean: success[, string: errMsg]
  
DESCRIPTION
  Sets the filter for a thread. Thread will gain control only if there will be appropriate signal.
  
EXAMPLES
  thread.setFilter(threadUid, "key_down")
  thread.setFilter(thread.getThread().uid, "key_down")
